  "text": "Remarkably, even though tissue hypoperfusion occurs frequently during high-risk surgery or in high-risk patients undergoing surgery [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] there is a lack of protocols for the perioperative management of high-risk surgical patients [CITATION_3] .",
